    <h1>Zero-Click Content</h1>
    <p class="description">Content — on social media or in search — that <strong>delivers its full value without requiring a click</strong>. Platforms algorithmically reward it with greater reach, making it a core strategy for brands building awareness without relying on referral traffic.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
